<p>Imperva will integrate the Distil Networks’ solution into the Imperva security stack to deliver complete protection for applications and APIs, wherever they reside REDWOOD SHORES, Calif. — June 4, 2019 — Imperva, Inc., the cybersecurity leader championing the fight to secure data and applications wherever they reside, today announced it has signed an agreement to acquire Distil [&#8230;]</p>
